a.description: Renders the correct article (a/an) for the specified word

an.description: Renders the correct article (a/an) for the specified word

A.description: Renders the correct article (a/an) for the specified word

An.description: Renders the correct article (a/an) for the specified word

image.description: Renders an image by the given path. Supports images embedded in the game code (e.g. trait icons)

pronounload.description: Assigns to the variable passed as second parameter, an object containing the pronouns for the specified actor

message.description: Renders an "spoiler tag", i.e. a clickable link (text passed as first argument) that toggles the visibility of the contained code

exp.description: Renders a value stylized as a Friendship amount

friendship.description: Renders a value stylized as a Friendship amount

prestige.description: Renders a value stylized as a Prestige amount

money.description: Renders a value stylized as a money amount: green if positive, red if negative

moneyloss.description: Renders a value stylized as a money amount. Opposite of 'money' macro: red if positive, green if negative

rep.description: Represents an actor or entity name along with small icons for busy/idle status, skill focuses, etc

nameof.description: Prints the name of the unit, in bold, without tooltips

name.description: Prints the name of the unit. Unlike <<rep>>, no tooltip is shown

levelof.description: Prints the level of the unit

titlelow.description: Prints the title of the unit, e.g., "generalist"

uequipslot.description: Prints the equipment worn on this slot. E.g., The drink spilled on your <<ueqeuipslot $unit.player 'legs'>>

ufriend.description: Print the friendship status between two units, e.g., friend, acquaintance, or rival

utheirrel.description: Print 'their relationship', e.g.: 'his friend' or 'her father'

unamerel.description: Print 'name's relationship', e.g.: 'Bob's sister' or 'Bob's friend'

ubodyall.description: Print 'muscular body covered with leather armor' or 'furry body covered in nothing'

ubreastsall.description: Print 'giant breasts with equipment' or 'tiny breasts with equipment'

unipplesall.description: Describes the unit nipples, including clothed status

uflavor.description: Print the bodypart full flavor text, if it has any. Example, <<uflavor $unit.player 'wings'>> will print the wing's flavor text if the unit has wings

uequipment.description: Print equipment description, e.g., 'bondage slutty armor' or 'valuable combat armor'

urace.description: Outputs the name of the actor's race

uhomeland.description: Outputs the region homeland of the actor, e.g., Eastern Deserts or The Mist

uweapon.description: Prints the unit's weapon, e.g., 'sword' or 'Excalibur'

uaweapon.description: Prints the unit's weapon, with an article. E.g., 'a sword' or 'an axe'

uadj.description: Prints an adjective from the unit, e.g., 'naughty' or 'tall'

uadjgood.description: Prints a positive adjective of the unit, e.g., 'smart'

uadjbad.description: Prints a negative adjective of the unit, e.g., 'stupid'

uadv.description: Prints an adverb of the unit, e.g., 'calmly'

uadvcare.description: Prints an adverb of the unit suitable for caring for a unit, e.g., 'gently, generously' but not `cruelly, violently`

uadvabuse.description: Prints an adverb of the unit suitable for abusing / attacking a unit, e.g., 'violently, evilly' but not `kindly, generously`

ustriptorso.description: Prints a sentence where the unit strips down from their upper body equipment, if any

ustriplegs.description: Prints a sentence where the unit strips down from their lower body equipment, if any

ustripanus.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever is filling their anus, if any

ustripgenital.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever is filling their vagina or blocking their dildo, if any

ustripvagina.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever is filling their vagina, if any

ustripdick.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever equipped on their dick, if any

ustripnipple.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever equipped on their nipples, if any

ustripmouth.description: Prints a sentence where the unit pulls whatever equipped on their mouth, if any

uslaverstripall.description: Prints a sentence where the unit strips everything if any

upunishreason.description: Prints a half-sentence giving a reason for punishing unit. Example use: 'You punish Bob because <<upunishreason $g.bob>>'

upraisenoun.description: Prints a praise-able noun of the actor. E.g., bravery, or handsomeness

uinsultnoun.description: Prints a insult-able noun of the actor. E.g., foolishness, or stupidity

uhobbyverb.description: Prints a verb about the unit's hobby. E.g., reminiscing about his past, or cooking

ustripshirtand.description: E.g., 'strips his shirt and'. Returns empty string if not wearing shirt

ustrippantsand.description: E.g., 'strips his pants and'. Returns empty string if not wearing pants

ustripmouthand.description: E.g., 'unfasten his gag and'. Returns empty string if not wearing mouth

ustripeyesand.description: E.g., 'removes his blindfold and'. Returns empty string if not wearing eyes

ustripanusand.description: E.g., 'pull out his buttplug and'. Returns empty string if not wearing anus

ustripgenitaland.description: E.g., 'unlock his chastity cage and'. Returns empty string if not wearing genital

ustripequipmentand.description: E.g., 'strips his armor and'. Returns empty string if naked

uneedrescue.description: Prints a sentence hinting that you ned to rescue unit with a Rescuer. Example: '<<uneedrescue $g.bob>>, before worse things happen'

urescuenow.description: Prints a sentence hinting that you ned to rescue unit now. Example: '<<uneedrescue $g.bob>> at once'

ubodyswap.description: Prints a sentence describing the transformations that the first unit undergoes to become the second unit

uinsultrape.description: Gives a speech where the first unit insults the second unit during a rape

unitcard.description: Prints the unit card of this unit

upetwhine.description: Prints a full dialogue about a pet humanlike whining.
